## PHP (Windows Herd + Git Bash)

**`php` is not on PATH** until `export PATH="/d/laravel13.x/bin:$PATH"` (see `docs/WINDOWS_HERD_GITBASH.md`).

```bash
export PATH="/d/laravel13.x/bin:$PATH"
cd examples/<project> && php artisan test
```

**Example UI:** `npm run dev` → open **`APP_URL` from `.env`** (e.g. `http://clone-the-fb-nav.test`), not :5173. `new-example` runs `herd link` automatically.
